摘  要
随着互联网技术的快速发展和电子商务的蓬勃兴起，传统农产品销售模式正面临深刻变革。本文设计并实现了一个基于SpringBoot框架的农产品销售系统，采用前后端分离的B/S架构，后端使用SpringBoot 3.4 + MyBatis-Plus + Spring Security + MySQL技术栈，前端使用Vue.js + Element UI框架。系统实现了用户管理、商品管理、订单管理、购物车、物流管理、评价管理、收藏管理、库存管理、内容管理和数据统计等核心功能模块，支持管理员、商家和普通用户三种角色。通过JWT实现无状态身份认证，采用Redis缓存提升系统性能，集成阿里云OSS实现文件云存储。系统具有良好的用户体验、较高的安全性和可扩展性，能够有效满足农产品线上销售的业务需求。
关键词：SpringBoot；农产品销售；电子商务；Vue.js；前后端分离



Abstract
With the rapid development of Internet technology and the booming of e-commerce, the traditional agricultural product sales model is facing profound changes. This paper designs and implements an agricultural product sales system based on the SpringBoot framework, adopting a B/S architecture with front-end and back-end separation. The back-end uses SpringBoot 3.4 + MyBatis-Plus + Spring Security + MySQL technology stack, and the front-end uses Vue.js + Element UI framework. The system implements core functional modules including user management, product management, order management, shopping cart, logistics management, review management, favorites management, inventory management, content management, and data statistics, supporting three roles: administrator, merchant, and regular user. Stateless identity authentication is implemented through JWT, Redis cache is used to improve system performance, and Alibaba Cloud OSS is integrated for cloud file storage. The system has good user experience, high security, and scalability, which can effectively meet the business needs of online sales of agricultural products.
Keywords: SpringBoot; Agricultural Product Sales; E-commerce; Vue.js; Front-end and Back-end Separation



